# Kvadrat

Vectorizes bitmap images by converting each pixel into polygons and merging regions with the same color.

| Bitmap                                        | SVG                                            |
| --------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------- |
| <img src="tests/00/input.png" width="100%" /> | <img src="tests/00/output.svg" width="100%" /> |

